00:00:16.210 --> 00:00:19.590
And then we've got Paul Frazee from Blue Sky

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:19.940
.

00:00:19.950 --> 00:00:23.000
So I'm going to let him take it away.

00:00:23.010 --> 00:00:26.320
All right.

00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:27.600
Welcome.

00:00:27.610 --> 00:00:29.750
Oh, yeah, we do need the mic.

00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:32.120
All right.

00:00:32.130 --> 00:00:32.860
Welcome, everyone.

00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:33.960
Thank you so much for being here.

